Package Included: 4PCS nylon wig caps and 2PCS mesh wig caps. Total 6pcs. Note: The nylon wig caps have 2 bags and each bag have 2pcs wig cap. (2 wig caps packed together in one paper board). The mesh wig caps also have 2 bags, but each bag only have 1pcs wig cap. (One paper board only have one wig cap).
Nylon Wig Cap: The nylon wig cap is made of high quality nylon material with great elasticity, one size fits most hair styles and sizes. Thick and wide elastic band, protect your skin from the itchy lace front and prevent wig cap and wig from slipping.
Mesh Wig Caps: Mesh net design is breathable and sweat-absorption which makes you feel more comfortable even in summer. Not easy to break, prolong the using time. One size fits most people due to the great elasticity.
Natural looking- Lightweight and ultra-thin which can put your hair in order naturally and trimly; Natural color will not be easily noticed and provide a natural looking. Help you create a variety of styles. Not only fit women, but also men, kids.
Convenient to use- Easy to wear and take off. Washable and reusable that can keep the wig and your hair clean. Help you hold your hair in place easily and comfortable. It is an essential tool for Halloween, makeup party, cosplay, etc.
